			<tr>
				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">I've played a Cleric for 66 Levels, a Magician for 65 Levels, and a Beastlord for 68 Levels.  Who is my main?  The Beastlord?  Why?  Because of Slow.  Period.
<br />

<br />
As content moves forward, most, if not all, groups are required to have a slower, or face needing incredible amounts of healing to keep someone alive, in which case they would also need significant group downtime.  Remember, no slower in a group means no Enchanter, Shaman, or Bard.
<br />

<br />
This is another lovely bit of SoE design, and has the same type of issue we now have with Complete Healing.  Either the game becomes trivial to play with it, or impossible to play without it.
<br />

<br />
Why shouldn't Beastlords be nerfed?  For the sake of having another class available for groups who need a slower.  For the sake of raiding, Beastlords have a significantly better survival chance on an initial slow resist than an Enchanter or Shaman -- two classes who are also key in debuffing the mobs as well.
<br />

<br />
What about mages?
<br />
Well, put bluntly, we can slow, but without high-end gear, and especially weapons, the Mage is going to bring quicker kills to the group.  IF a group already has a slower, what benefit does the Beastlord bring to a group?  Well, we are a melee DPS class.  Groups with an Enchanter and no shaman can still receive the benefit of the IoS / Kragg series of spells.  Groups with a shaman instead can benefit from the Spiritual Dominion mana regen spells.
<br />

<br />
Personally, I'd like to see us given the group-version of our current STR / DEX / STA buffs, at their same amount of power.  Just the group version.
<br />

<br />
If someone is looking for a slower, and they see a shaman and a beastlord looking for a group, most will still take the shaman.  Why?  The shaman makes all the other classes better at what they do with their far superior buffs.  However, if no Shamans are available, no Enchanters are available, and no Bards are available, isn't it nice to have a 4th choice?<br />_________________<br /><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=539574" target="_blank" class="postlink">[68 Feral Lord] Sylventhe Kor`Vashal &lt;Final Destiny&gt;</a>
<br />
<a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=539570" target="_blank" class="postlink">[66 Archon] Wyndam Kindheart &lt;Final Destiny&gt;</a></span><span class="gensmall"></span></td>
			</tr>
		</table></td>
	</tr>
