				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">I view the two classes are about = in the ability to solo.  Bsts melee and therefore need a way to reduce the amount of damage the mob inflicts on them hence slow.  Mages get DS so the more hits the pets takes, the quicker the mob goes down.
